branchCategory.name: 10-SZ
branchCategory.description: <P>Series 10-SZ3000 is a 5 port solenoid valve, body ported type with a cassette style manifold. The 10-SZ series offers high reliability and long life of 50 million cycles or more. The connector entry direction can be changed from top to side with a simple operation. Low power consumption and a fast response time of 10ms are obtained with a unique pilot valve construction. </P>
